data.text:
Amir Johnson - Points

Amir Johnson scores a career high 32 points (2013)

On December 08, 2013, Amir Johnson set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 32 points in Toronto's road win against LA Lakers, 94-106. He also had 10 rebounds, 1 assist, 2 steals and 2 blocks. He shot 14/16 from two, 0/1 from three, shooting at 82.4% from the field. He also shot 4/4 from the free-throw line.

Amir Johnson - Rebounds

Amir Johnson grabs a career high 21 rebounds (2013)

On March 15, 2013, Amir Johnson set his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 21 rebounds in Toronto's home win against Charlotte, 92-78. He also had 12 points, 1 assist, 2 steals and 3 blocks.

Amir Johnson - Assists

Amir Johnson gives a career high 6 assists (2011)

On February 04, 2011, Amir Johnson tied his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 6 assists in Toronto's home win against Minnesota, 111-100. He also had 19 points, 12 rebounds, 3 steals and 2 blocks.

Amir Johnson - Steals

Amir Johnson has a career high 5 steals (2013)

On February 03, 2013, Amir Johnson set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 5 steals in Toronto's home loss against Miami, 85-100. He also had 2 points, 7 rebounds and 2 assists.

Amir Johnson - Blocks

Amir Johnson blocks a career high 7 shots (2008)

On February 13, 2008, Amir Johnson tied his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 7 blocks in Detroit's home win against Indiana, 96-80. He also had 8 points, 9 rebounds and 1 assist.

Amir Johnson - Efficiency

Amir Johnson records a career high 41 efficiency rating (2013)

On December 08, 2013, Amir Johnson set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 41 efficiency in Toronto's road win against LA Lakers, 94-106. He also had 32 points, 10 rebounds and 1 assist.
